stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Created: create()
    Created --> Active: Initial state
    Active --> Updated: update()
    Updated --> Active: Changes saved
    Active --> Archived: archive()
    Archived --> Active: unarchive()
    Active --> Favorited: favorite()
    Favorited --> Active: unfavorite()
    Archived --> Deleted: delete()
    Deleted --> [*]

    note right of Created
        Objects are created with
        type, title, properties
    end note

    note right of Active
        Objects can be queried,
        related, and modified
    end note

    note right of Archived
        Soft delete - hidden
        from default queries
    end note
